§I ASSERT-MAPPING
  A05.1 runner refuses bare exit-0 · no obs    →  verify.rs gate · refuses if observable=true ∧ no events
  A05.2 cssl_test_observe registration helper  →  events.rs · macro/fn that emits JSONL
  A05.3 empty user_main fails A05.1            →  examples/empty_user_main.cssl · CI verifies

